{"tid":1573300,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"休班狗可能係其他人扮","createTime":"2019-09-16T03:03:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T04:24:53.000Z","uid":49898,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"dab8dbdbf5f72febf60e196a30fd32fd22bb3bbc","tid":1573300,"uid":49898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T03:03:44.000Z","msg":"《睇黎港共想暗地裡大屠殺》<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1557672\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1557672</a><br />\n<br />\n我之前已經講過派警棍依樣野<br />\n最大問題係警權過大+便衣+無證+武器（警棍）<br />\n狗隊依個行動係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">放任鄉黑藍可以全面武裝</span></span><br />\ne.g. <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/112755063407258/posts/127510221931742?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F112755063407258%2Fposts%2F127510221931742%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=qpM4horlrIen4ao1f4l1xUbB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=294ddc2e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/112755063407258/posts/127510221931742?sfns=mo</a><br />\n即係你估唔到條街有邊個係狗，邊個會打你<br />\n<br />\n而且依個現象係可以伸延去更<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">恐怖嘅方向</span></span><br />\n特別係大家開始習慣<br />\n便衣+警棍=狗<br />\n拉上私家車=返狗屋<br />\n<br />\n當你將依啲無關係嘅野想像成有關係嘅話<br />\n係非常危險<br />\n<br />\n如果我係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">強姦犯，殺人犯</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">又著普通衫</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">又唔會有證</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">又揸伸縮棍</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">又有私家車</span></span><br />\n咁我係街是旦捉人<br />\n如果俾我捉果個<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">覺得我係狗就唔反抗</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n隔離啲市民又<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">以為我係狗就唔阻止</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁我咪好順利捉到獵物<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以我覺得首先被捕人俾人捉要<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大叫先，引多啲人黎</span></span><br />\n而其他人要<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">救人</span></span>，第一個叫救人，之後叫跟，就衝去救<br />\n<br />\n而家係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">三不管時期</span></span>，我地要靠自己人互相幫助<br />\n<br />\n你地有咩睇法？"},{"pid":"8f29b4b1de134bb16bf891101cc3e59b86759e27","tid":1573300,"uid":49898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T03:06:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"baf9feeca5ad04edf00b3efa9d51003aec5d23cf","tid":1573300,"uid":263186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T05:26:09.000Z","msg":"休班狗當藍絲咁打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dd12469562cd9cca7bc7bff913ee154d62d7496","tid":1573300,"uid":34755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"baf9feeca5ad04edf00b3efa9d51003aec5d23cf","tid":1573300,"uid":263186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T05:26:09.000Z","msg":"休班狗當藍絲咁打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T03:55:12.000Z","msg":"便衣 休班當藍斯咁打"},{"pid":"db968ec139b84492aaf17cd456135516441a0565","tid":1573300,"uid":135011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"baf9feeca5ad04edf00b3efa9d51003aec5d23cf","tid":1573300,"uid":263186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T05:26:09.000Z","msg":"休班狗當藍絲咁打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T03:56:48.000Z","msg":"一律當藍絲處理<br />\nHit and run"},{"pid":"65a470739637c50b664a95c274995e18d4ed6aab","tid":1573300,"uid":282777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T04:24:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f25bb41b5f5a402080e9442311d16b5f584e44e5","tid":1573300,"uid":282777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T04:24:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}